How come the color works but not the text align?
```&lt;style&gt;

	.team-member h3 {
		text-align: {{ module.style.membername.textalignment_field }};
		color: {{ module.style.membername.color_field.color }};
	}
		.team-member p {
		text-align: {{ module.style.position.textalignment_field }};
		color: {{ module.style.position.color_field.color }};
	}

&lt;/style&gt;```
